metadata.description:
Beautiful and captivating. Her inner light shines the brightest.

The name Eve means living; so I wanted to bring life to her beautiful face.

This is a hand drawn frame animation. Each layer is drawn individually to create movement and light. It takes hours to create, but I enjoy working in this way because the imperfections make the final piece a surprise and completely unique. 


2000 x 2000px MP4
